The paper involves the use of deep imitation learning to learn policies for fabric smoothing, which requires understanding of fabric states and dynamics. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Robotics (cs.RO), Computer Vision (cs.CV), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories.
